---
title: 404 - 页面未找到
date: 2025-05-02 20:33:17
layout: page
comments: false
permalink: /404.html
---

<div class="error-container">
  <h1>404</h1>
  <p>您访问的页面不存在或已移动</p>
  <a href="/" class="home-link">返回首页</a>
</div>

<style>
.error-container {
  text-align: center;
  margin: 100px auto;
  max-width: 600px;
}
.home-link {
  display: inline-block;
  margin-top: 20px;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  background: #3498db;
  color: white;
  border-radius: 4px;
}
</style>

